{
  "page": "Gerold Dayne",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne_of_High_Hermitage\" title=\"House Dayne of High Hermitage\"><img alt=\"None (Dorne).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/50px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/75px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/100px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Gerold Dayne<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Darkstar</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne_of_High_Hermitage\" title=\"House Dayne of High Hermitage\"><img alt=\"None (Dorne).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/50px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/75px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/100px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Gerold_dayne_by_bellabergolts.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Gerold dayne by bellabergolts.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/97/Gerold_dayne_by_bellabergolts.jpg/350px-Gerold_dayne_by_bellabergolts.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/97/Gerold_dayne_by_bellabergolts.jpg/525px-Gerold_dayne_by_bellabergolts.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/97/Gerold_dayne_by_bellabergolts.jpg/700px-Gerold_dayne_by_bellabergolts.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Darkstar by Bella Bergolts ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nDarkstar</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_High_Hermitage\" title=\"Knight of High Hermitage\">Knight of High Hermitage</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne_of_High_Hermitage\" title=\"House Dayne of High Hermitage\">House Dayne of High Hermitage</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_270_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">270</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_274_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">274&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\nPrincess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>        \n<p><b>Gerold Dayne</b>, known as <b>Darkstar</b>, is the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_High_Hermitage\" title=\"Knight of High Hermitage\">Knight of High Hermitage</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne_of_High_Hermitage\" title=\"House Dayne of High Hermitage\">His house</a>  is a lesser branch<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">Daynes</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a>, and he is a cousin to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edric_Dayne\" title=\"Edric Dayne\">Edric Dayne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Gerold\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Gerold</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Gerold\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Gerold</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Gerold_Dayne\" title=\"Category:Images of Gerold Dayne\">Images of Gerold Dayne</a></div>\n<p>Gerold is in his late twenties.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> A handsome man, he has a clean-shaven face with an aquiline nose, high cheekbones, dark <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_eyes\" title=\"Purple eyes\">purple eyes</a>, and a strong jaw. Gerold has collar-length thick silver hair, divided by a streak of midnight black.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Despite his beauty and valor, Gerold is a cruel man with angry eyes. He is jealous of his famous cousin, the late Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a>, who was the <a href=\"/index.php/Sword_of_the_Morning\" title=\"Sword of the Morning\">Sword of the Morning</a>. Darkstar wields a <a href=\"/index.php/Longsword\" title=\"Longsword\">longsword</a>. He prefers to drink unsweetened <a href=\"/index.php/Lemon\" title=\"Lemon\">lemonwater</a> instead of <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">summerwine</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>At some point, Gerold was one of the lovers of <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Darkstar_and_Myrcella_by_Preston_Stone.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/Darkstar_and_Myrcella_by_Preston_Stone.jpg/350px-Darkstar_and_Myrcella_by_Preston_Stone.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"253\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/2/2d/Darkstar_and_Myrcella_by_Preston_Stone.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Darkstar_and_Myrcella_by_Preston_Stone.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Darkstar attacks <a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a>, by Preston Stone © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Gerold allies himself with Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> when she attempts to crown Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a> in place of her younger brother, King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a>. At <a href=\"/index.php/Shandystone\" title=\"Shandystone\">Shandystone</a>, Arianne admits to her other conspirators that she only included Darkstar for his fighting prowess and his keep, <a href=\"/index.php/High_Hermitage\" title=\"High Hermitage\">High Hermitage</a>. Gerold is skeptical of Arianne's plan to provoke <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_Regent\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen Regent\">Queen Regent</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Arianne's party is surprised at the <a href=\"/index.php/Greenblood\" title=\"Greenblood\">Greenblood</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Areo_Hotah\" title=\"Areo Hotah\">Areo Hotah</a>, who orders them to surrender. Gerold agrees since they are outnumbered, but Myrcella's bodygyard, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arys_Oakheart\" title=\"Arys Oakheart\">Arys Oakheart</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>, rides to his death in an attack on Areo. Amidst the fighting, Gerold attempts to kill Myrcella.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Her horse rears, however, and Darkstar succeeds only in slicing off her ear and scarring her face.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> He escapes Areo's guards by riding into the sands of Dorne.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Myrcella is taken to <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>, where Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Caleotte\" title=\"Caleotte\">Caleotte</a> saves her life. Arianne ponders whether her plan had been betrayed by Darkstar or by another of her conspirators.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Swann\" title=\"Balon Swann\">Balon Swann</a> arrives at Sunspear with the <a href=\"/index.php/Mountain%27s_skull\" title=\"Mountain&#39;s skull\">Mountain's skull</a>. Under Arianne's instruction, Myrcella has blamed Darkstar, not Areo, for the death of Arys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Arianne's father <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Prince of Dorne</a>, sends <a href=\"/index.php/Obara_Sand\" title=\"Obara Sand\">Obara Sand</a> with Balon to hunt Gerold at <a href=\"/index.php/High_Hermitage\" title=\"High Hermitage\">High Hermitage</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> Cersei thinks that Darkstar is a catspaw of her brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>, whom she already blames for the deaths of her first son, King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon</a>, and her father, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>While traveling to the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>, Arianne and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a> discuss Gerold. Arianne feels that Obara and Areo can kill Darkstar, although Daemon is skeptical. Arianne is regretful for ever trusting Gerold, thinking that he was so handsome she had not believed half the stories told about him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-arianne1_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-arianne1-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Gerold\">Quotes by Gerold</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Gerold\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg/350px-Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"247\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg/525px-Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg/700px-Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mathia_Arkoniel_DarkstarDayne.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Darkstar, by Mathia Arkoniel</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>If I led a quarter of a million men to death, would they call me Gerold <a href=\"/index.php/Garin_the_Great\" title=\"Garin the Great\">the Great</a>? I shall remain Darkstar, I think. At least it is mine own.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Gerold to <a href=\"/index.php/Garin_(orphan)\" title=\"Garin (orphan)\">Garin</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I was weaned on venom, Dalt. Any <a href=\"/index.php/Viper\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Viper\">viper</a> takes a bite of me will rue it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Gerold to <a href=\"/index.php/Andrey_Dalt\" title=\"Andrey Dalt\">Andrey Dalt</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Myrcella</b>: Are you the <a href=\"/index.php/Sword_of_the_Morning\" title=\"Sword of the Morning\">Sword of the Morning</a> now?<br />\n<b>Gerold</b>: Men call me Darkstar, and I am of the night.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a> and Gerold</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Gerold\">Quotes about Gerold</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Gerold\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Darkstar_by_Preston_Stone.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/Darkstar_by_Preston_Stone.jpg/350px-Darkstar_by_Preston_Stone.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/0/0b/Darkstar_by_Preston_Stone.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Darkstar_by_Preston_Stone.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Darkstar hones his sword, by Preston Stone © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>He is <a href=\"/index.php/Highborn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Highborn\">highborn</a> enough to make a worthy consort, she thought. <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Father</a> would question my good sense, but our children would be as beautiful as <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonlords\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragonlords\">dragonlords</a>. If there was a handsomer man in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, she did not know him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>By tradition the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> were the finest <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> in all the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> ... but Darkstar was Darkstar.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>You were a fool to make him part of this. Darkstar is the most dangerous man in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>. You and he have done us all great harm.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Ser Gerold is more a <a href=\"/index.php/Viper\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Viper\">viper</a> than your uncle ever was. Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn</a> could see that he was <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poison</a>, he said so more than once. It's just a pity that he never got around to killing him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-arianne1_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-arianne1-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Sand\" title=\"Daemon Sand\">Daemon Sand</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">Poison</a>, yes. Pretty poison, though.<sup id=\"cite_ref-arianne1_10-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-arianne1-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gerold_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Gerold_Dayne\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Gerold Dayne</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafgerold_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Gerold Dayne.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/1394\">US Signing Tour (Denver, CO)</a>, November 22, 2005</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\">5.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\">5.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-4\">5.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-5\">5.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-6\">5.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-7\">5.7</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-8\">5.8</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-9\">5.9</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_21\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 21\">Chapter 21</a>, The Queenmaker.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">6.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">6.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\">6.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 40\">Chapter 40</a>, Princess In The Tower.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">7.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\">7.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, The Watcher.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">8.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\">8.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_54\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 54\">Chapter 54</a>, Cersei I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Epilogue_(A_Dance_with_Dragons)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Epilogue (A Dance with Dragons)\">Epilogue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-arianne1-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-arianne1_10-0\">10.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-arianne1_10-1\">10.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-arianne1_10-2\">10.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne I</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404055056\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.189 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.453 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2544/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12084/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 22056/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4247/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 9056/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.250/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.57 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  415.316      1 -total\n 82.87%  344.160      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 82.47%  342.497      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.50%   51.908     23 Template:Ref\n 10.84%   45.034     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  7.59%   31.528     23 Template:Ref/core\n  6.30%   26.179      6 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.73%   19.656      8 Template:Quote\n  2.13%    8.852      1 Template:See_also\n  2.00%    8.290      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5505-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404055056 and revision id 325226\n -->\n",
